  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Full 13-factor assessment performed. Decision record records Accepted; however, one or more credibility factors carry achievedLevel strictly below requiredLevel, constituting a rebutting defeater (W-AR-02).",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-absolute-threshold",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cou2-vad-hemolysis-credibility",
